{"tid":485804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"低頭玩手機！索女長腿「插」渠蓋","createTime":"2017-12-01T09:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T11:23:51.000Z","uid":75969,"like":112,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"e544e49edb0359e5f4dc221a9a1ef4167f14a7be","tid":485804,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/150/15048189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F150%2F15048189.jpg&h=981d51b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/imgs/image/150/15048187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fimgs%2Fimage%2F150%2F15048187.jpg&h=8d974383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">智能手機普及之後，衍生了新的族群「低頭族」，他們去到邊手機都不會離身，不論行路、搭車、食飯，無時無刻都低頭看、低頭玩手機，正因為「低頭族」唔睇路，造成不少的意外。河南鄭州市近日有一名長腿索女，疑因低頭玩手機，於是「叉錯腳」，其中一條修長的美腿牢牢地「插」入路面的一個臭水溝的鐵蓋，進退不能。<br />\n<br />\n網傳照片所見，該名身穿短裙的長腿索女已「插」入間條的渠蓋，坐在地上，而現場有一名疑似渠務工人手執「鐵筆」，嘗試將鐵條撬開。當「鐵筆」插落撬開之際，長腿索女的同行女子便從後協助，將其拉出，可憐長腿索女臉有難色，顯得十分痛苦，而當時也吸引了不少人圍觀，場面極為尷尬。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171201/photo/bkncn-20171201080228759-1201_05011_001_02b.jpg?20171201080537\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171201%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171201080228759-1201_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20171201080537&h=4809d31d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171201/bkncn-20171201080228759-1201_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171201%2Fbkncn-20171201080228759-1201_05011_001.html&d=GSdaCmPx%2BB3i8tDtzJQ1YF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b5efb136\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171201/bkncn-20171201080228759-1201_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a53ebdbf925e5d96029499c5495ec241dd78874d","tid":485804,"uid":156331,"li